Yes, I believe I can entrust
you with that information...

rows.label: tlk44400287_02_msg0002
rows.name:
The ancient science of Luxuria,
passed down through generations...remains
unchanged to this day.

rows.label: tlk44400287_02_msg0003
rows.name:
That's right. We have in fact not
advanced one jot technologically. We
have not evolved as has Superbia.

rows.label: tlk44400287_02_msg0004
rows.name:
If by chance something
unprecedented, not chronicled
by our ancestors, were to happen...

rows.label: tlk44400287_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Then we would fall like
a house of cards. Just
like Theospiti Temple...
